f:S^1 \rightarrow \mathbb{R}
E[f(Z)]=\int_{0}^{2\pi}{f(e^{i\theta})\frac{1}{2\pi}}d\theta=\frac{1}{2\pi i}\int_{S^1}{\frac{f(z)}{z}}dz,
z=e^{i\theta}
\frac{dz}{d\theta}=ie^{i\theta}
\frac{dz}{iz}=\frac{dz}{ie^{i\theta}}={d\theta}
